query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('apache-spark-mllib',
'api-design',
'cross-validation',
'dropbox-api',
'flutter-layout',
'html5-audio',
'noclassdeffounderror',
'pom.xml',
'powermock',
'reportviewer',
'uistoryboard',
'webpack-dev-server');
